{"tid":904042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大生畢業禮撐政治犯","createTime":"2018-11-16T04:28:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T05:15:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":24,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6c3daaba5cd6e8a4c9f31e1d3bb5d69fd1e236ab","tid":904042,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T04:28:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181116/20547347\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181116%2F20547347&d=sDlfSdw5COyVDtaB0INsC49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=d4dc220e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181116%2F20547347&h=9dd80346\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181116/20547347</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月16日 <br />\n<br />\n中大生畢業禮撐政治犯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181116/large/16la4p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181116%2Flarge%2F16la4p2.jpg&h=774c5944&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n約60名社工系學生拉起「悼香港 念政治犯」橫額表達對言論自由受打壓的不滿。謝榮耀攝 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港中文大學昨日舉行畢業典禮，數十名應屆畢業學生在典禮期間發起抗議行動，除了在演奏國歌期間拉起橫額之外，亦在頒授學位期間站立默哀，並高呼抗議的口號，藉以表達對於言論自由不斷被打壓的關注，以及為近年來遭受政治檢控的政治犯發聲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拉「悼香港」橫額默哀<br />\n<br />\n畢業典禮甫開始，會場演奏國歌，前中大學生會會長王澄烽聯同文學院畢業生，於國歌演奏期間，拉起印有「今日國歌法，明日廿三條」的橫額，並且舉起印有「為何不愛國亦是罪名，為何不肅立是件壞事情」字句的標語，藉以抗議國歌法及香港言論自由遭受打壓的現況。<br />\n<br />\n王澄烽表示，近年目睹言論及思想自由的空間不斷地收窄，所以希望藉此表達對於捍衞自由的呼聲，「我哋呢幾年見到民選議員被DQ，最近又發生馬凱、馬建、巴丟草事件，都反映緊𠵱家香港嘅政治審查同自由面對好大問題」，王澄烽又表示，未來國歌法將會被提交上立法會，「係香港政府同中國政府聯手打壓異見人士的言論自由」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，頒授社會科學學位期間，亦有約60名社工系學生在會場站立默哀，並且拉起印有「悼香港 念政治犯」字眼的橫額，以及高呼「拒絕政治檢控，釋放香港政治犯」等抗議口號。應屆社工系畢業學生張展翹表示，希望能夠以社工系學生的身份，為被檢控及入獄的政治犯發聲，「我哋入學嗰一年係雨傘運動，之後見到一批又一批嘅參與者被檢控同埋入獄，嚟緊陳健民教授都將會因為佔中案接受審訊，我哋今次嘅抗議係希望可以為政治犯發聲」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李雨夢  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n憂影響子女　家長無意轉校<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n港鐵兩促解決剪鋼筋問題　禮頓監工：唔記得"},{"pid":"d914b4397a54ed3517f5d53fdc55303910f06259","tid":904042,"uid":66943,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T04:28:54.000Z","msg":"笑晒既屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4c7c5c26eea677bb37973d25a70eefb723021c","tid":904042,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T04:55:15.000Z","msg":"好立即釋放梁天琦同其他被屈暴動罪的義士喇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83acc91191352915c39784a84f343d20a118103","tid":904042,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:02:37.000Z","msg":"社工系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ca0fd2226ab266393a1de12a6218c4b8d844ea","tid":904042,"uid":77626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:04:41.000Z","msg":"拉哂佢當地坐牢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a6374010c2efbc9ab75d0e553bbdf224c98d67","tid":904042,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci